---
title: Sweet and Sour Style Vegetables with Star Anise Basmati Rice
description: We love good Sweet & Sour Veg with Basmati Rice and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-and-sour-style-vegetables-9b057571-55f2d5cb.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/sweet-and-sour-style-vegetables-5f633457c0a70e18f0529b3a-d3dcc564.pdf
